      "title": "[DC] lightproud@🐱light’s-nest: Morimens is more than a Lovecraftian work. What it really hopes to speak about i",
      "summary": "Morimens is more than a Lovecraftian work. What it really hopes to speak about is that small flicker of humanity that endures even in the depths of despair. And I hold the naive hope that one day, developers and players everywhere can find a better way of talking to one another, and can truly cherish each other from the heart. Everything this work has been through is, to me, the best proof that this is possible.\n\nI have always loved you all. No matter what comes next, and whether you trust me or not, I will keep giving you the very best that I — and the whole BIAV team — have to offer, just as I always have.\n\nMay the Silver Key guide us.",
